text: Denise Maree Roche (born 9 July 1963) is a New Zealand politician. She was a member of the Waiheke Local Board and the New Zealand House of Representatives, where she represented the Green Party of Aotearoa New Zealand from 2011 to 2017. Roche was born in 1963 in Helensville. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand politicians
